    <item>
      <title>查看與下載 KakaoPay 收款 QR 碼的方法</title>
      <link>https://blog.moneyskilltalk.com/zh/kakaopay-qr-code-download/</link>
      <guid>https://blog.moneyskilltalk.com/zh/kakaopay-qr-code-download/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 May 2025 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        MoneySkillTalk 為您介紹如何查看與下載 KakaoPay 的收款 QR 碼
      
      </description>
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>MoneySkillTalk 為您介紹如何查看與下載 KakaoPay 的收款 QR 碼。</p><hr><center><a href="https://www.mkttalk.com/tools/kakaopay-link-generator/" target="_blank"><img src="https://hellotblog.files.wordpress.com/2020/04/kakaopay-receive-qr-code-01-600.jpg" class="shadow" style="width:450px; max-width:100%;" alt="MoneySkillTalk"></a></center><p>首先打開 KakaoTalk 手機應用程式，然後在「More」選單中點選上方的「Scan」按鈕。</p><hr><center><a href="https://www.mkttalk.com/tools/kakaopay-link-generator/" target="_blank"><img src="https://hellotblog.files.wordpress.com/2020/04/kakaopay-receive-qr-code-02-600.jpg" class="shadow" style="width:450px; max-width:100%;" alt="MoneySkillTalk"></a></center><p>當進入「Scan」畫面後，點選下方的「Receive」選項。</p><hr><center><a href="https://www.mkttalk.com/tools/kakaopay-link-generator/" target="_blank"><img src="https://hellotblog.files.wordpress.com/2020/04/kakaopay-receive-qr-code-03-600.jpg" class="shadow" style="width:450px; max-width:100%;" alt="MoneySkillTalk"></a></center><p>點擊「Receive」後，會顯示您個人的 KakaoPay 收款 QR 碼。</p><p>「輸入金額」為可選項目。若輸入金額，將生成固定金額的 QR 碼；若不輸入金額，系統將自動生成可讓對方自由輸入金額的 QR 碼。</p><p>點擊 QR 碼下方的下載圖示，即可下載所產生的 QR 碼圖片。</p><hr><center><a href="https://www.mkttalk.com/tools/kakaopay-link-generator/" target="_blank"><img src="https://hellotblog.files.wordpress.com/2020/09/kakaopay-link-generator-usage-guide-cover-completed-800x560-1.png" style="max-width:100%;" alt="MoneySkillTalk"></a></center><p>KakaoPay 行動轉帳連結生成服務(KakaoPay Mobile Transfer Link Generator)是一項線上服務，可透過下載的收款 QR 碼輕鬆產生 KakaoPay 行動轉帳連結。</p><p>將生成的連結嵌入網站或部落格後，客戶只需點擊一次，即可直接向您的 KakaoPay 帳戶匯款，無需額外流程。</p><hr><center><a href="https://www.mkttalk.com/tools/kakaopay-link-generator/" target="_blank">KakaoPay 行動轉帳連結生成服務 (KakaoPay Mobile Transfer Link Generator) : 了解詳情<br>www.mkttalk.com/tools/kakaopay-link-generator/</a></center><hr><center><div id="promo-code" style="font-weight:bold; padding:10px;" class="allowContent"></div></center><hr><!-- [參考] <a href="./../kakaopay-link-generator-mobile-qr-code/" target="_blank">如何透過 KakaoPay 轉帳連結輕鬆收款（適合自由工作者、個人創業者等）</a> --><!-- *** --><p>如對服務有任何疑問，歡迎隨時透過 <strong><a href="https://www.moneyskilltalk.com/kr/kakao/" target="_blank">KakaoTalk</a></strong> 與我們聯繫！</p><script type="text/javascript">  const url = 'https://www.desource.kr/app/kakaopay-link-generator/api/';  fetch(url)    .then(res => res.json())    .then(value => {        if ( ( value[0] !== null ) && ( value[0] !== '' ) && ( value[0] !== undefined ) ) {             document.getElementById('promo-code').innerHTML = '<i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> 優惠碼 ( ' + value[0]['discount_percentage'] + '% ) : <span  style="font-weight:bold; color:#c82333;">' + value[0]['promo_code'] + '</span>';         }  })</script>]]></content:encoded>
      
